title: The Cariboo Trail (1950 Western) Gateway to Gold, Greed and Glory ! Randolph Scott & Gabby Hayes

sources.title: The Cariboo Trail (1950 Western) Gateway to Gold, Greed and Glory ! Randolph Scott & Gabby Hayes
sources.description:
Jim Redfern, a cattleman chasing his dream of a ranch in British Columbia’s untamed wilderness, drives his cattle up the Cariboo Trail. Joined by his reluctant partner Mike Evans and luckless prospector Grizzly Winters, Jim braves the Cariboo Trail during a gold rush, clashing with ruthless local boss Frank Walsh. After a brutal cattle stampede orchestrated by Walsh leaves Mike maimed and Jim’s dreams shattered, Jim turns to gold mining for survival. But with Walsh determined to destroy him, Jim must fight back to stake his claim—not in gold, but in a future built on grit and resilience.

The Cariboo Trail is a 1950 American Western film directed by Edwin L. Marin

Main actors:
Randolph Scott - Jim Redfern
George "Gabby" Hayes - Oscar aka Grizzly
Bill Williams - Mike Evans
